    "headline": "Qualcomm Earnings Release Available on Company’s Investor Relations Website",
    "summary": "SAN DIEGO, April 29, 2026--Qualcomm Incorporated (NASDAQ: QCOM) today announced the Company’s financial results for its second quarter of fiscal 2026 through an earnings release that is available on the Qualcomm Investor Relations website at https://investor.qualcomm.com/financial-information. The earnings release will also be furnished to the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) on a Form 8-K and will be available on the SEC website at http://www.sec.gov.",
